      <title>历史性干旱导致赞比亚每天供电时间缩短至三小时</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/historic-drought-cuts-zambia-s-power-supply-to-three-hours-a-day</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赞比亚的电力危机进一步加剧，数十年来最严重的干旱抑制了占电力总产量 85% 的水力发电量，目前家庭每天的供电时间不足三个小时。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/historic-drought-cuts-zambia-s-power-supply-to-three-hours-a-day</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 08:26:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
